{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_LOG_120.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x19,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Logy? What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sophie. I was actually thinking about making new weapons soon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "New weapons!? Wow, that's exciting! What kind of weapons?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "You know, the ones I talked about before? Weapons that help people travel."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "The ones that anyone can use, right? So you're going to make the weapons of your dreams?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's not really that simple."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It's easy to talk about weapons that anyone can handle, but actually forging them is difficult."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If it's a weapon that a child or elderly person can use, it needs to be very light, but it can't be fragile either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...I've been thinking about it for a while, but I'm not coming up with any good ideas."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see... Is there anything I could do to help?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You're always helping me, so I want to cooperate with whatever I can."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Is it really okay? In that case, could you bring me something that would inspire me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "H-huh!? That's really vague, I don't really understand..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... Maybe it should be something you don't see very often now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Like what...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "You use materials like metals, hard lumber, ores, minerals, and gems to make weapons, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Among all those things, there's some materials that you used to find all the time, but don't see very often anymore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know. But why aren't they seen often now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Who knows? There are lots of possible reasons, but the biggest is probably just sheer scarcity of the material."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, if you find any old and rare materials like that, can you bring them to me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, this seems difficult..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "It's only if you happen to find them. I'll try thinking of other ways too. Just keep an eye out, alright?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I-I understand... I'll try searching..."
        }
    ]
}